<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft zum
                            <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> vicztum in Nidern Payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch ein
                                <expan>arm<ex>er</ex></expan> knecht <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
                        Fricz, etwenn bey der <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> <expan>Krom<ex>er</ex>in</expan> zu Eschembach
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, fürbracht hab, daz er gen uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> sey, daz er bey
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> scheden süll
                            <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein und uns bitt, den des zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>wissen</expan>, wan ir maint, daz er uns
                                <expan>unrechtl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und auf das
                                <expan>schreibe<ex>n,</ex></expan> daz uns ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getan hat, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
                        sache <expan>v<ex>er</ex>wissen</expan> und im
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> keins argen
                            <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Dorothee. </ab>
</div>
